<p>7/9/17 On skirmishing stunt all day having lunch out on field. After tea went out for blackberries.<br/>8/9/17 Battalion sports all day. Left just after dinner for billets &amp; washed hdcfs then bathed in stream alongside billet. Heard going to line on Tuesday. Few more casuals arrived from Havre. Heavy fog til 9am. Went blackberrying after tea.<br/>9/9/17 Sunday &ndash; beautiful sunshine, not a cloud to be seen. On &frac12; rations today. Numbers of aeroplanes about. 2pm walked into Lumbres with Ashwood. Bought maps of France in there, then had steak &amp; eggs for tea &ndash; cost 3 francs. Left 6pm &amp; arrived back 7.30pm. Sent ppcards to Australia &amp; England in green envelope also with 2 whiz-bangs.<br/>10/9/17 Lewis Gun all day.</p>
